title: DDFP 328: Defining moments of 2014 NFL season
itunes:title: DDFP 328: Defining moments of 2014 NFL season
description:
Shek and Handsome Hank react to the latest fall out of Super Bowl XLIX and discuss the defining moments from the 2014 NFL season including the Browns drafting Johnny Manziel, Carson Palmer's injury, Peyton fizzling out in December and Le'Veon Bell's injury in week 17.
